{"lemma":"مَطْلَعٌ","slug":"مَطْلَعٌ","root":"ط.ل.ع","root_slug":"ط-ل-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ط-ل-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مَطْلَع","root":"طلع","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n26957"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B7%D9%92%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"beginning, onset, outset"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the first line of a qasida or ghazal"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"rising of any celestial body","examples":[{"text":"Coordinate term: مَغْرِب (maḡrib)"},{"text":"سَلَامٌ هِيَ حَتَّىٰ مَطْلَعِ الْفَجْرِ","english":"It is all peace until the break of dawn."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"any place that celestial bodies rise.","examples":[{"text":"حَتَّىٰٓ إِذَا بَلَغَ مَطۡلِعَ ٱلشَّمۡسِ وَجَدَهَا تَطۡلُعُ عَلَىٰ قَوۡمٖ لَّمۡ نَجۡعَل لَّهُم مِّن دُونِهَا سِتۡرٗا","english":"until he reached the rising ˹point˺ of the sun. He found it rising on a people for whom We had provided no shelter from it."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ladder, stairs"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of طَلَعَ (ṭalaʕa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"well-informed, acquainted with, cognizant of"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun and noun of place from the verb طَلَعَ (ṭalaʕa).\n\nDerived from the active participle of اِطَّلَعَ (iṭṭalaʕa, “to take insight”)."},"ipa":["/matˤ.laʕ/","/matˤ.liʕ/","/mutˤ.tˤa.liʕ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26957","headword_ar":"مَطْلَعٌ","root":"TlE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maToliEN","text_ar":"مَطْلِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"are inf. ns.: and signify also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"time"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of rising"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the sun [&c.]: (S, O, K: [see 1, first sentence:]) but by Fr the former is explained as meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rising,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the latter as meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place of rising:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and some of the Basrees say that when one reads"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hat~aY maToliEi Alfajori","text_ar":"حَتَّى مَطْلِعِ الفَجْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the last verse of ch. xcvii. of the Kur], with kesr to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"l","text_ar":"ل"},{"kind":"text","text":", the meaning is, ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"until"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the time of rising"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the dawn"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (O, TA:) [the pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTaAliEu","text_ar":"مَطَالِعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"places"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"times"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of rising"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the sun [&c.]. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTolaEu Aljabali","text_ar":"مَطْلَعُ الجَبَلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The place of ascent of the mountain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA laka maTolaEa AlA^akamapi","text_ar":"هٰذَا لَكَ مَطْلَعَ الاَكَمَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is present before thee;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as near to thee as if thou hadst to ascend for it the hill."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTolaEu AlqaSiydapi","text_ar":"مَطْلَعُ القَصِيدَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The beginning of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qSydp","text_ar":"قصيدة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ode"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b4-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muT~alaEN","text_ar":"مُطَّلَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["O","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}